        <updateDate>2023-02-24T12:00:16Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safer Heat Act of 202&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;b&gt;3&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the Consumer Product Safety Commission to establish safety standards for portable heating devices, including a requirement that a device shuts off at a threshold determined hazardous by the commission. The commission is authorized to enforce these standards.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
